response.plainText: Chicago is the third most populous city in the  United States . Its metropolitan area is sometimes called  Chicagoland. Chicago is the  seat  of  Cook County , a small part of the city extends into  DuPage County. It was incorporated as a city in 1837. Chicago is listed as an alpha+ global city. The best-known nicknames for the city include  Windy City  and  Second City. The City of Chicago was the fastest growing city in the world for several decades.
